data.description: Full Moon Farm is 4.79 and features a 3 bedroom 2 bath gorgeous farm house built in 1920. Enjoy a sip of tea on the wrap around front porch. The floor to ceiling stone fireplace in the living room is breathtaking with custom book shelves on each side. A staircase leads upstairs to the cozy loft area and walk in storage areas. The cook's kitchen (renovated in 2022) boast a walk in pantry, SS appliances, and an Eat-In area overlooking the outdoor flower garden and patio. Large bedrooms with a spa-like owner's bath (updated in 2017). Relaxing sunroom displays an electric fireplace and exits off to a back deck that is great for entertaining (redone in 2018). The double carport is oversized and detached from the house. Beautiful landscaping. Serene and very private. Horses are allowed. Plumbing replaced and front porch redone in 2015. HVAC replaced in 2016 and duct system replaced in 2021. New roof in 2018. New hot water heater in 2021 with added hot water system. Electrical system maintained and 2 new service panels.
